      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising, showroom-grade standard. This specimen represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in pristine condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of rigorous preservation. Every detail has been meticulously cared for, ensuring that it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. An investment-grade offering for those who prioritize absolute quality and automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
